                                   TO  JOB-SHELLMSG
           CALL    "ORCSJOB"       USING
                                   ORCSJOBKANRIAREA  
                                   JOBKANRI-REC
      *
           MOVE    "RECE420"           TO  RECE42PARA-FILE-ID
           MOVE    WRK-PARA-TERMID     TO  RECE42PARA-TERMID
      *
           MOVE    "RECE430"           TO  RECE43PARA-FILE-ID
           MOVE    WRK-PARA-TERMID     TO  RECE43PARA-TERMID
